00:57:12,000 --> 00:57:16,000
 And the people who hear it are proved to be true.

1082
00:57:16,000 --> 00:57:18,000
 But at the same time,

1083
00:57:18,000 --> 00:57:21,000
 God uses the miracle of the Holy Spirit

