00:57:28,000 --> 00:57:34,000
 The function of the miracle is to witness.

1087
00:57:34,000 --> 00:57:38,000
 The miracle is not the way of God.

1088
00:57:38,000 --> 00:57:41,000
 You have to hear the way to believe.

1089
00:57:41,000 --> 00:57:44,000
 The miracle is to witness.

