00:59:20,000 --> 00:59:22,000
 Jesus Christ is the Son of God.

1118
00:59:22,000 --> 00:59:24,000
 Jesus Christ is the Holy Spirit.

1119
00:59:24,000 --> 00:59:30,000
 So the whole miracle is pointing to Jesus Christ, the Savior.

