01:00:30,000 --> 01:00:33,000
 There were a group of very intellectual Pharisees

1139
01:00:33,000 --> 01:00:37,000
 who saw Jesus' miracles and knew that he came from God.

1140
01:00:37,000 --> 01:00:38,000
 Why?

1141
01:00:38,000 --> 01:00:41,000
 He said, "We"

