01:00:59,000 --> 01:01:01,000
 This is the function of miracles.

1149
01:01:01,000 --> 01:01:03,000
 Miracles are not the purpose.

1150
01:01:03,000 --> 01:01:07,000
 This is the purpose of the miracles.

