01:01:07,000 --> 01:01:10,000
 Jesus Christ came from God.

1152
01:01:10,000 --> 01:01:12,000
 When this happened,

1153
01:01:12,000 --> 01:01:16,000
 they heard Jesus' truth.

1154
01:01:16,000 --> 01:01:18,000
 So Jesus answered,

1155
01:01:18,000 --> 01:01:20,000
 "I tell you the truth.

