01:07:58,000 --> 01:08:01,000
 which are pleasant to hear,

1291
01:08:01,000 --> 01:08:03,000
 but soon they will no longer be heard.

1292
01:08:03,000 --> 01:08:06,000
 Some soils are deep.

1293
01:08:06,000 --> 01:08:10,000
 They feel it's good to try to be a Christian,

1294
01:08:10,000 --> 01:08:13,000
 but they find that the world is better,

1295
01:08:13,000 --> 01:08:16,000
