1296
01:08:16,000 --> 01:08:19,000
 They no longer go to the roadside.

1297
01:08:19,000 --> 01:08:22,000
 The good soil is the small part.

1298
01:08:22,000 --> 01:08:25,000
 Jesus Christ said that there are few people who have enough.

